### [John Chapter 2](../../../bib/kjv/joh002.htm#001.md)

[John](../../../bib/kjv/joh001.htm#001.md)

<span class="margnote"><span id="an_000">joh 2:0</span></span>

Overview

[Joh 2:1](../../../bib/kjv/joh002.htm#001.md), Christ turns water into
wine; [Joh 2:12](../../../bib/kjv/joh002.htm#012.md), departs into
Capernaum, [Joh 2:13](../../../bib/kjv/joh002.htm#013.md). and to
Jerusalem, [Joh 2:14](../../../bib/kjv/joh002.htm#014.md). where he purges
the temple of buyers and sellers; [Joh
2:18](../../../bib/kjv/joh002.htm#018.md), He foretells his death and
resurrection; [Joh 2:23](../../../bib/kjv/joh002.htm#023.md), Many believe
because of his miracles, but he will not trust himself with them.

